full_text: Using the @nflfastR Expected Points model (which is trained on NFL data so not perfect here), having the ball on the 7 with 17s left and 2 TOs gives you an EP of 4.18 whereas the tackle loses Towson 2 points (plus negligible EP) so the return is MUCH worse #NFLVerse https://t.co/IIjCKCB16f
